title: Issue with 3.5 mm jack connector through C type USB cable
content:
There is an issue with the audio being played through 3.5 mm jack which can be connected through C type USB Cable.

Already the device, PIXEL 2XL, has been reset. Also the cable is working perfectly fine on other device so there is no issue with the cable as well. 

One fine day the cable stopped working. Seems to be some software glitch or patch update. Request your urgent assistance on same.
